{"tid":2407220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國考慮3月8日開返學，新研究希望小童能終身免疫","createTime":"2021-02-14T00:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T00:48:43.000Z","uid":391702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"540ff4932bfb330d4da17a9c2fe1d8932cb625b5","tid":2407220,"uid":391702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T00:20:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56054637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-56054637&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=3c02975a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-56054637&h=85143ccc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-56054637</a><br />\n<br />\nboris會喺2月22日作最後決定，佢話前境樂觀，目前有近千五萬人接種咗第一期疫苗，頭四類高危人仕大致完成第一針接種，希望3月8日可俾學生返學，之後局部性俾賣必需品以外嘅店舖開返門，之後輪到餐飲同酒店業。<br />\n<br />\n另外英國會同5歲以上小童試驗新疫苗，希望可以好似種牛荳咁，令佢地終身免疫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XHF6OX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XHF6OX.jpg&h=a61814a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baf8f35e026d0b4017dbba1e8ff16b1d42f69621","tid":2407220,"uid":328235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"molamola <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成年人都未知immunity last 幾耐，咁快FF小童終身免疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一期trial 收300個test immunogenicity ，有撚排先到population scale <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b614081cdf3ef40f6d1c1a9318628b40c7dde0d","tid":2407220,"uid":391702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf8f35e026d0b4017dbba1e8ff16b1d42f69621","tid":2407220,"uid":328235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T00:29:03.000Z","msg":"molamola <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gi